# Frontend env values are provided by the deployment host (Vercel/Netlify/Cloudflare Pages).
# Do NOT commit the legacy JWT-shaped Supabase publishable key here — it was the root cause
# of the "Legacy API disabled" issue baked into the stale Lovable production bundle.
#
# Required at build time (set in the host's environment variable UI):
#   VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://aizkqajrzkvwuobisnzr.supabase.co
#   VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=<current sb_publishable_* key from Lovable Cloud → Backend → API keys>
#   VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID=aizkqajrzkvwuobisnzr
SUPABASE_URL="https://aizkqajrzkvwuobisnzr.supabase.co"
VITE_SUPABASE_URL="https://aizkqajrzkvwuobisnzr.supabase.co"
VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID="aizkqajrzkvwuobisnzr"
